# source:   athena
# purpose:  Executable bit coherence -- detects shebang/git-mode mismatches that
#           cause CI-only ruff EXE001/EXE002 failures.
# baseline: Empty. Any findings indicate files whose git mode must be fixed.
# columns:  file	violation
rf_listener.py		shebang_not_executable	has shebang but git mode is 100644 (needs: git update-index --chmod=+x)
